<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Purchase Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; color:
      #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; } .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } .header { text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px; } .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; color:
      #007BFF; } .content { line-height: 1.6; } .content p { margin: 0 0 10px; }
      .content .info { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 10px; border-radius:
      5px; } .footer { text-align: center; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 14px;
      color: #999; } .footer a { color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Purchase Order Confirmation</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <strong>{{billingName}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>Thank you for your order from
          <strong>{{schoolName}}</strong>. We are pleased to confirm your
          purchase order:</p>

        <div class="info">
          <p><strong>Purchase Order No:</strong> {{purchaseOrderNo}}</p>
          <p><strong>Publication:</strong> {{publicationName}}</p>
          <p><strong>Created At:</strong> {{createdAt}}</p>
          <p><strong>Updated At:</strong> {{updatedAt}}</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Books</h2>
        <ul>
          {{#each books}}
            <li><strong>{{this.bookName}}</strong>
              (Qty:
              {{this.qty}}, Code:
              {{this.code}}, Standard:
              {{this.textbookStd}})</li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>

        <p>If you have any questions regarding your order, feel free to reach
          out to us.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Sahyog Team</p>
        <p><a href="https://popcase.in">Visit Our Website</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>